---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout lang="yue" title="Xiaosi Huang · 數據可視化作品集">
  <section class="pt-12 pb-20 md:pt-18 md:pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl px-8">
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500">DATA PORTFOLIO</p>

      <h1 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight">
        用數據講故事，
        <span class="text-sky-600">將洞察化作影響</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- 這段是正文敘述：已修正用詞和標點，前後都沒有多餘空格 -->
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-600">
        專注做 Tableau 視覺化、儀表板設計同商業分析。呢度可以睇到我精選嘅作品、方法同筆記。
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
        <a href="/projects" class="px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium hover:bg-sky-700 transition">睇作品</a>
        <a href="/about" class="px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-700 font-medium hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 transition">關於我</a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">視覺化儀表板</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-70">增長、營運同市場關鍵指標</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">數據敘事</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-70">由 KPI 連起故事，推動業務決策</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">方法同復盤</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-70">結構化思考模板同最佳實踐</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
